ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: interesting class, learn a lot about democratic govt structures. Maybe a good idea to rename the course. would totally recommend this to someone else.

I would certainly recommend the class to a fellow student, as it contained a broad, informative spectrum of reading with interesting weekly class discussions. The workload was manageable, and the final paper flexible enough to allow the development of a real personal interest.
Yes, I would recommend this course to anyone with an interest in Europe.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: made me think about internal workings of governments differently
While not very relevant to completing my history MA, the class was incredibly useful looking ahead to my future path after academics.
